  * debian/rules: Ship /etc/udev/scripts/removable.sh again, the absence of
    this broke automounting on half the machines out there. (Ubuntu #13520)

 -- Martin Pitt <martin.pitt@ubuntu.com>  Tue, 16 Aug 2005 22:49:26 +0200

