    as requested by the udftools maintainer. (Closes: #274110)
  * scsi-devfs.sh: create .../disc instead of .../disk. (Closes: #276484)
  * Added a workaround to mount the tmpfs even if .udev.tdb exists in the
    static /dev/ directory.

